2
00:00:19,936 --> 00:00:24,024
<i>"If a man has a conscience,
he will suffer for his mistake.</i>

3
00:00:24,941 --> 00:00:28,236
<i>That will be his punishment
as well as his prison."</i>

4
00:00:30,071 --> 00:00:31,781
