This is not you.

18
00:01:06,983 --> 00:01:09,069
Everything I told you is true.

19
00:01:09,652 --> 00:01:11,821
Beck, Henderson,

20
00:01:12,781 --> 00:01:14,032
Delilah...

21
00:01:15,533 --> 00:01:16,576
