52
00:02:54,132 --> 00:02:56,134
[Love]<i> I knew right away, in my gut,</i>

53
00:02:56,217 --> 00:02:58,469
<i>I recognized something in you. And, hey,</i>

54
00:02:58,553 --> 00:03:01,973
<i>smart, sexy, funny,</i>

55
00:03:02,056 --> 00:03:06,436
<i>a little darkness that made you
less storybook, more real.</i>

56
00:03:07,187 --> 00:03:09,397
<i>I started to fantasize again.</i>

57
00:03:10,481 --> 00:03:13,193
<i>When you pulled away,
I told myself, "I can fix him."</i>

58
00:03:15,278 --> 00:03:16,988
<i>For a while, it was working.</i>

59
00:03:17,071 --> 00:03:18,615
<i>I showed you how to heal.</i>

60
00:03:19,782 --> 00:03:22,535
<i>Oh, you were stronger than I knew.</i>

61
00:03:23,328 --> 00:03:28,499
<i>I showed you what I wanted
by showing you what I didn’t want.</i>

62
00:03:29,125 --> 00:03:32,128
<i>When you stood by me, united,</i>

63
00:03:33,087 --> 00:03:36,049
