than the family I was born into.</i>

64
00:03:36,132 --> 00:03:37,717
[Love imitates snarl]

65
00:03:39,093 --> 00:03:40,303
I wolf you.

66
00:03:40,887 --> 00:03:42,013
I wolf you too.

67
00:03:45,516 --> 00:03:47,477
Maybe I got a little obsessed.

68
00:03:48,228 --> 00:03:52,190
