174
00:10:13,571 --> 00:10:15,156
I mean, it wouldn't...

175
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:17,908
if my family didn't basically own
the LAPD.

176
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:21,162
It's the way the <i>au pair</i> got cleaned up.

177
00:10:21,245 --> 00:10:27,001
Ellie is going to emerge stronger,
smarter,

178
00:10:27,585 --> 00:10:29,420
- and better off.
- Like Forty?

179
00:10:29,503 --> 00:10:32,048
- Watch it.
- Okay, Ellie, then.

180
00:10:33,215 --> 00:10:35,676
What kind of sick mind
thinks forcing a teenager

181
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:38,429
