to love you.</i>

220
00:13:01,822 --> 00:13:03,908
<i>I don't know what to feel, Love.</i>

221
00:13:05,117 --> 00:13:06,243
<i>But I know what to do.</i>

222
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:08,370
[Joey] <i>Are you in trouble for the gun?</i>

223
00:13:08,954 --> 00:13:10,080
Not at all.

224
00:13:10,164 --> 00:13:12,666
So, we can be together forever?

225
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:22,092
I love you so much, Joey. So, so much.

226
00:13:22,259 --> 00:13:23,928
[knocking on door]

227
00:13:25,554 --> 00:13:29,225
[Joe] <i>It isn't hard to convince somebody
you love them</i>

228
00:13:29,642 --> 00:13:31,477
<i>if you know what they want to hear.</i>

229
00:13:38,359 --> 00:13:39,819
